{
  "stem": "7744.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And even today, with all that I do and all the educational stuff that I do, I tell many people.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "I tell them that the gaps that I have-- the gaps that are missing-- I have never caught up with.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "I have been able to compensate, but I haven't caught up the gaps.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And-- and many times I think, you know, once I retire, which will be soon maybe, maybe I'll do something still to catch up some of the gaps.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "But I doubt it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, he helped put on my boots one day on Brunswick someplace within the Y.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I came-- I came with another fellow to the dance, but he was very nice, and he helped me.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we befriended each other.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it was also one of the boys in the club, and I went out with a couple boys quite seriously before Howard.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I met Howard.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And sometimes he says to me, in-- in all honesty, I think you got married because you wanted to get out of the house.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How old were you when you got married?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was 19-- 19, 20, 19.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I married in 1951.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Yeah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It wasn't easy living with my aunt.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It wasn't easy.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It wasn't easy because I wasn't able to show any appreciation.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I didn't have it in me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I think that-- I think that-- I think that there was a tremendous hardness.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think there was a feeling I went through, and-- and-- and some things are coming to me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You are my aunt.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't love her.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I had no relationship with her.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She had this old-fashioned family feeling, and she-- she loved me in her way, and she wanted to help me.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
